snippet.title: Best VGM 619 - 3D Dot Game Heroes - Wilderness
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 694 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=70oTg2go0XU
Best VGM 1887 - https://youtu.be/jhsNQ6r2fHE
Best VGM 2078 - https://youtu.be/BQRKQ-CQ27U

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation 3
3D Dot Game Heroes (2010)
Wilderness
Shinji Hosoe, Ayako Saso, Yousuke Yasui, Shoichiro Sakamoto, Teruo Taniguchi, Takahiro Eguchi & Norihiro Furukawa
